OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FPatches of low cloud and any
OL,6,Ffog will soon clear to leave a dry day
OL,7,Facross the region. Further cloud will
OL,8,Ffeed in from the northwest during the
OL,9,Fday, though there will be some warm
OL,10,Fspells of sunshine.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FThe evening looks mainly dry
OL,13,Fwith a few clear intervals, though
OL,14,Fcloud will increase for a time
OL,15,Fovernight bringing patchy rain.
OL,16,FTurning dry and a little clearer again
OL,17,Flater.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
