OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FEarly sunshine will give way
OL,6,Fto thickening cloud and outbreaks of
OL,7,Frain on Saturday morning, accompanied
OL,8,Fby fairly brisk winds. A breezy and
OL,9,Fshowery afternoon will follow.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FSunday
OL,12,Fwill be a fresher, still breezy day
OL,13,Fwith sunshine and scattered showers.
OL,14,FStaying more changeable than of late
OL,15,Finto early next week. Some sunshine,
OL,16,Fthough rain at times too.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
